Title: Crane Butterfly Valves F624 lever operated butterfly valve PN16 2"
Description: Suitable for applications requiring Level 3 C3 (medium) corrosion protection, this maintenance-free Crane F624 fully-lugged PN16 butterfly valve incorporates 2" connections and a ductile iron body. Title: Hattersley Fig 100EXT DZR ball valve (BSP) PN25 50mm
Description: The Hattersley Fig 100EXT lever operated ball valve is easy to install, compact and lightweight and is supplied with 50mm BSP tapered connections. Made of DZR brass, this robust valve offers full flow with minimum turbulence in the open position and bubble tight closure in the closed position. A ball valve is a type of quarter-turn valve featuring a hollow, perforated ball that pivots to control the flow of a fluid. Title: Grundfos Magna 3 40-150 F 250 circulating pump 1 x 230V PN6/10
Description: Ideal for creating high performance heating and cooling systems, the Grundfos MAGNA3 40 - 150 F single phase circulator pump is suitable for new installations and refits, offering excellent efficiency and built-in communication capabilities. With a canned rotor, this pump is a maintenance-free integral unit with no shaft seal and just two gaskets for sealing, while bearings are lubricated by the pumped liquid. Wirelessly connecting with the Grundfos GO Remote app, for advanced reporting and monitoring, MAGNA3 is suitable for mixing loops, heating and air conditioning surfaces, ground source heat pumps and small chillers and includes fieldbus communication via CIM modules as well analogue and digital inputs and configurable relays.
